      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tenzir/claude-plugins/contents/plugins%2Fformatter%2Fchangelog%2Freleases%2Fv1.2.0%2Fnotes.md?ref=3e75e2b3bfba7c70afdfcee27e4208ccc7bafaf7",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+This release adds ESLint support for JavaScript and TypeScript files, automatically fixing linting issues after every edit.\n+\n+## \ud83d\ude80 Features\n+\n+### ESLint support for JavaScript and TypeScript\n+\n+The formatter plugin now runs ESLint with `--fix` on JavaScript and TypeScript files when available, automatically fixing linting issues after every Write or Edit operation.\n+\n+*By @mavam and @claude.*"
